    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Papers or paperlike materials, often decorative in nature, made primarily for attachment to walls and ceilings but sometimes applied to other surfaces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
